org.mpxj.mpp

Class UserDefinedFieldMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mpxj.mpp.UserDefinedFieldMap

  • public class UserDefinedFieldMap
extends Object
    This class is used to generate a mapping between a set of user defined fields and a set of custom fields. This allows schedules exported from applications which make use of user defined fields to be imported into Microsoft Project with the values originally in user defined fields preserved and made available in Microsoft Project in custom fields.
